"title": "5013: heart, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5013: heart, divine",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The inner thoughts, feelings, will and desires of God, as they are revealed in Scripture and in Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Aspects of the heart of God</h2>\n<h3>His joy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:17\">ZEP 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:9\">DEU 30:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:11\">PSA 147:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:4\">PSA 149:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1\">ISA 42:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:24\">JER 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:22\">LUK 3:22</a></p>\n<h3>His compassion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:8\">HOS 11:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:21\">GEN 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:19\">EXO 33:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6-Exod34:7\">EXO 34:6–34:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:38-Ps78:39\">PSA 78:38–78:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:8-Ps103:11\">PSA 103:8–103:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:44-Ps106:45\">PSA 106:44–106:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:10\">ISA 54:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:44-Matt5:45\">MAT 5:44–5:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:15\">ROM 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3\">2CO 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:11\">JAS 5:11</a></p>\n<h3>His affection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:7-Deut7:8\">DEU 7:7–7:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:3\">1KI 9:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:16\">2CH 7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:14\">PSA 148:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:11\">ISA 40:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:3\">JER 31:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:41\">JER 32:41</a></p>\n<h3>His intentions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:11\">PSA 33:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:35\">1SA 2:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:13\">JOB 10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:4\">ISA 63:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:20\">JER 23:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:11\">JER 29:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:24\">JER 30:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:22\">ACT 13:22</a></p>\n<h3>His inner pain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:6\">GEN 6:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:9-Isa63:10\">ISA 63:9–63:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:8\">HOS 11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:30\">EPH 4:30</a></p>\n<h2>The heart of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>His joy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:11\">JHN 15:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21\">LUK 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:13\">JHN 17:13</a></p>\n<h3>His compassion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:36\">MAT 9:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:14\">MAT 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:32\">MAT 15:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:34\">MAT 20:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:13\">LUK 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:41\">LUK 19:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:35-John11:36\">JHN 11:35–11:36</a></p>\n<h3>His affection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:1\">JHN 13:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:29\">MAT 11:28–11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21\">MRK 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:20\">JHN 21:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:8\">PHP 1:8</a></p>\n<h3>His inner pain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:5\">MRK 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:44\">LUK 22:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:35-John11:36\">JHN 11:35–11:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:38\">JHN 11:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:27\">JHN 12:27</a></p>\n<h2>God's people are to reflect God's heart</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:10\">COL 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:14\">1SA 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:22\">ACT 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:15\">JER 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:27-Luke6:36\">LUK 6:27–6:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:49\">1CO 15:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:24\">EPH 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:17\">1JN 3:17</a></p>",
